OL,3,CBritain First march: Far right group
OL,4,Cgathers in Manchester amid counter
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FA protest by the Britain First far
OL,8,Fright group is underway in Manchester
OL,9,FCity centre, amid counter protests and
OL,10,Fa huge policing operation.
OL,12,FHundreds of officers are on hand for
OL,13,Fthe protest. The police presence was
OL,14,Fstepped up significantly after
OL,15,Fviolence flared at a previous Britain
OL,16,FFirst 'march for remigration' in
OL,17,FFebruary.
OL,19,FJust before 2:30pm on Saturday, police
OL,20,Freported two arrests of counter
OL,21,Fprotestors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
