OL,3,CBritain First march: Far right group
OL,4,Cgathers in Manchester amid counter
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FIn a statement posted to X, GMP said:
OL,8,F"Earlier, counter-protesters had
OL,9,Fattempted to break police lines and
OL,10,Fattempted to throw punches. PAVA spray
OL,11,Fwas deployed as a tactic instead of
OL,12,Fusing further additional force. There
OL,13,Fare no reports of any members of the
OL,14,Fpublic being injured."
OL,16,FOn Saturday afternoon, a large group
OL,17,Fgathered on Store Street underneath
OL,18,FPiccadilly station, before marching to
OL,19,FSt Peter's Square for a rally.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
