OL,3,CBritain First march: Far right group
OL,4,Cgathers in Manchester amid counter
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FA counter protest by a coalition of
OL,8,Fanti-racism groups calling itself
OL,9,FResist Britain First is also being
OL,10,Fheld in Piccadilly Gardens. Hundreds
OL,11,Fof counter demonstrators are expected.
OL,13,FVisitors to the city are being warned
OL,14,Fto expect some disruption to roads and
OL,15,FMetrolink services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
