OL,3,CBritain First march: Far right group
OL,4,Cgathers in Manchester amid counter
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FPolice have been given extra powers to
OL,8,Fdeal with trouble-makers during the
OL,9,Fprotests. A Section 34 dispersal order
OL,10,Fhas been put in place for the city
OL,11,Fcentre on Saturday, while a Section 60
OL,12,Forder gives officers enhanced stop and
OL,13,Fsearch powers and allows for the
OL,14,Fremoval of face coverings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
